data.description: Welcome to this charming home located in the highly desired Saraland school district. This lovely house features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for your family. One of the highlights of this home is the bonus space, which can be used as an office, dining room, game room, or an extra space for the family to hang out. This versatile area allows you to customize the space to fit your needs and lifestyle. Inside, you'll find fresh paint on the walls, giving the home a clean and modern feel. All appliances will remain, making the move-in process a breeze. Step outside into the large fenced back yard, ideal for children and pets to play freely and safely. The cozy outdoor living area provides a relaxing space to unwind and enjoy the beautiful weather. The well sought after neighborhood offers a peaceful and friendly atmosphere, perfect for creating lasting memories. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Call your agent today to schedule your personal tour, and experience the comfort and convenience this property has to offer!All updates per the seller. Listing company makes no representation as to accuracy of square footage; buyer to verify. 2024-02-01
